        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Kali122-kilavi">itu kāmañcālā iḷamaiyōḷvayiṟ piṉ kaḷavoḻukkam oḻukiya talaivaṉ iṭaiyiṭṭup pirintu toṉmuṟai maṉaiviyaroṭu puṇarcci yeyti iruntāṉāka, ataṉaiyaṟintu āṟṟāḷāya talaivi āṟṟāmai kaṇṭu viṉāya tōḻikku attalaivi avaṉoḻukukiṉṟavāṟun taṉṉeñcu avaṉ vayattatāyavāṟuṅ kūṟiyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en"></p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="Kali122">
                <l>kōtai yāyamu maṉṉaiyu maṟivuṟap </l>
                <l>pōteḻi luṇkaṇ pukaḻnala ṉiḻappak </l>
                <l>kātalcey taruḷātu tuṟantārmāṭ ṭētiṉṟic </l>
                <l>ciṟiya tuṉittaṉai tuṉṉācey tamarntaṉai </l>
                <l>palavunū ṟaṭukkiṉai yiṉaipēṅki yaḻutaṉai </l>
                <l>yalavalai yuṭaiyai yeṉṟī tōḻī;</l>
                <l rend="space">kēḷiṉi;</l>
                <l rend="space">māṇeḻiṉ mātar makaḷirō ṭamaintavaṉ </l>
                <l>kāṇumpaṇ pilaṉāta laṟiveṉmaṉ ṉaṟiyiṉum </l>
                <l>pēṇi yavaṉciṟi taḷittak kāleṉ </l>
                <l>ṉāṇi ṉeñca nekiḻtaluṅ kāṇpal;</l>
                <l rend="space">iruḷuṟa ḻiruṅkūntaṉ makaḷirō ṭamaintavaṉ</l>
                <l>ṟeruḷumpaṇ pilaṉāta laṟiveṉmaṉ ṉaṟiyiṉu</l>
                <l>maruḷi yavaṉciṟi taḷittak kāleṉ </l>
                <l>maruḷi neñca makiḻtaluṅ kāṇpal;</l>
                <l rend="space">oḷḷiḻai mātar makaḷirō ṭamaintava</l>
                <l>ṉuḷḷumpaṇ pilaṉāta laṟiveṉmaṉ ṉaṟiyiṉum </l>
                <l>pulli yavaṉciṟi taḷittak kāleṉ </l>
                <l>ṉalla ṉeñca maṭaṅkaluṅ kāṇpal;</l>
                <l rend="space">ataṉāl,</l>
                <l>yāma naṭunāṭ ṭuyilkoṇ ṭoḷitta </l>
                <l>kāma nōyiṟ  kaḻīiya neñcan </l>
                <l>tāṉavar pāṟpaṭṭa tāyi </l>
                <l>ṉāmuyir vāḻtalō nakainaṉi yuṭaittē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
                <l corresp="2">While [your] kajal eyes with the grace of buds lost [their] praised beauty</l>
                <l corresp="1">so that [your] garlanded companions and mother had knowledge [of it],</l>
                <l>you were disgusted a little, without reason, with the one who abandoned [you]</l>
                <l corresp="3f">without graciously making love [to you]. You abided doing [thing] without coming near.</l>
                <l corresp="5">Desperately lamenting, being one who piles up many hundreds, you cried.</l>
                <l>You are in confusion, you would tell [me], friend,</l>
                <l corresp="6-7">Listen now:</l>
                <l>I do know that he is without visible qualities,</l>
                <l>being suited to beautiful women of glorious grace. Even though knowing,</l>
                <l>at the time when he respected [me and] cared a little,</l>
                <l corresp="8-11">I see my shameless heart becoming emaciated. </l>
                <l>I do know that he is without perceptible qualities,</l>
                <l>being suited to women with tresses dark like darkness. Although knowing,</l>
                <l>at the time he graciously cared [for me] a little,</l>
                <l corresp="12-15">I see my heart rejoice in confusion.</l>
                <l>I do know that he is without memorable qualities,</l>
                <l>being suited to beautiful women with bright jewels. Even though knowing,</l>
                <l>at the time he embraced [me and] cared a little,</l>
                <l corresp="16-19">I see my unhappy heart fold.</l>
                <l corresp="20">Therefore,</l>
                <l>if [my] very heart that passes in love sickness</l>
                <l>that [it] conceals, taking sleep at midnight,</l>
                <l>falls to his share,</l>
                <l corresp="21-24">we living a life, ah, is very laughable.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
